CustomerId.description:
The Belvo ID of previously created customer that will make the payments to the beneficiary.

{% admonition type="warning" name="Customer from Payments-BR.V2" %}
  The provided customer ID must be one that was created using the `Payments-BR.V2` version of our API. For example, using either the Bank Account Details option when created the Payment Authorization, or the Create a Customer endpoint with the `X-Belvo-API-Resource-Version: Payments-BR.V2` header.
  If you provide an ID that is not `Payments-BR.V2` version compliant, you will receive the following error: `The customer does not exist or is invalid.`.
{% /admonition %}

